This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module toaster-app-config container toaster-app-config { leaf manufacturer { type toaster:DisplayString; default Opendaylight; } leaf model-number { type toaster:DisplayString; default "Model 1 - Binding Aware"; } leaf max-make-toast-tries { type uint16; default 2; } } The schema path to identify an instance is toaster-app-config/toaster-app-config To create instances of this class use ToasterAppConfigBuilder.
